    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras/1b96dc212adeca8e2f4a8da85cb88873.avif?t=1763280779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras_big/1b96dc212adeca8e2f4a8da85cb88873.avif?t=1763280779 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东方风Project</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>東方謎縁塔 ~ Forsaken Labyrinth.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阐幽赜书房的首次弹幕演出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生活少不了那些兼具活力和火力的弹幕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请全力提升装备、在弹幕中穿行，然后优雅起舞吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作拥有特殊的道具系统和装备兑换系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以收集特殊道具“联系力”，并用联系力兑换获取各种联系卡片来丰富游戏流程。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras/69c05c47ec25c03c507580e3c96ac31f.avif?t=1763280779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras_big/69c05c47ec25c03c507580e3c96ac31f.avif?t=1763280779 width=800 height=200 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瘟疫般的异常正在逐渐显现， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从人之里到妖怪之山都能感受到异变的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制造它的凶手究竟是谁，在哪里，为什么……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怀着不同的目的和心境，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类尝试着去发掘真相、并解决这一新的危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras/4577c7273d47aea182e26a741e13fe2a.avif?t=1763280779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227170/extras_big/4577c7273d47aea182e26a741e13fe2a.avif?t=1763280779 width=800 height=200 /></span>  *基础操作　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○上下左右（默认为方向键）：控制自机移动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○SHOT键（默认为Z键）：射击（长按连射）/确定 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○BOMB键（默认为X键）：符卡（有次数限制）/取消 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○SLOW键（默认为Shift键）：低速移动 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○PAUSE键（默认为ESC键）：暂停</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  *特殊操作 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○跳过对话：长按SHOT键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○高速重试：暂停界面按R键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○变速播放录像：按住SHOT键可以加速，按住SLOW键可以减速</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○切换窗口/全屏模式：Alt + Enter </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ○截图：Home键</p>",
